{"tid":2352438,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"EXO邊伯賢，首次個人演唱會也獲得成功…吸引120個國家觀眾觀看","createTime":"2021-01-04T04:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T06:42:45.000Z","uid":256952,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5ac663fbf480f23606d7bb3f88f3fd416e10c08a","tid":2352438,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:40:10.000Z","msg":"全世界120個國家都觀看了EXO伯賢的首次個人演唱會，證明了其作為&ldquo;solo歌手&rdquo;的強大影響力。<br />\n創下&ldquo;solo專輯百萬銷售記錄&rdquo;的EXO伯賢通過世界最初線上專用付費演唱會&ldquo;Beyond LIVE&rdquo;圓滿結束了首次個人演唱會。<br />\n韓國時間3日下午3點開始通過NAVER V LIVE直播的付費演唱會&ldquo;Beyond LIVE - BAEKHYUN : LIGHT&rdquo;以EXO世界觀中伯賢的超能力&ldquo;光&rdquo;為主題，展現了多種體裁的音樂和表演，以及華麗的AR和圖像效果相結合的演出。<br />\n據經紀公司SM娛樂透露，此次演出是伯賢的首場個人演唱會，包括韓國在內的美國、中國、日本、泰國等全世界120個國家的約11萬名觀眾一起觀看了演出。演出期間，&ldquo;BAEKHYUNBeyondLIVE&rdquo;、&ldquo;BAEKHYUN1stConcert&rdquo;等Hashtag還佔據了法國、荷蘭、俄羅斯、越南、印度尼西亞等國家的Twitter實時趨勢一位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dHj3O7o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdHj3O7o.jpg&h=78861c79&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ks8wdz8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKs8wdz8.png&h=0f09c293&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bu7XTA0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBu7XTA0.png&h=7138c1ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ada2b363f7b73296b4bfcdf058b238177e6a8c28","tid":2352438,"uid":205928,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:40:48.000Z","msg":"無人識佢"},{"pid":"99803a47380de53dbdf42af4f6ecc111ae831ae5","tid":2352438,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ada2b363f7b73296b4bfcdf058b238177e6a8c28","tid":2352438,"uid":205928,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:40:48.000Z","msg":"無人識佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:41:23.000Z","msg":"哈酸"},{"pid":"fb4c5862fab93fda9d10151dad74ea8595ff2d37","tid":2352438,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0